om/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Prodigy-Yungblud-Offspring@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Prodigy-Yungblud-Offspring@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Prodigy-Yungblud-Offspring@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Prodigy-Yungblud-Offspring@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Prodigy-Yungblud-Offspring@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 2024 年 Rock For People 音乐节已宣布几位新艺术家，其中<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-offspring">The Offspring</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yungblud">Yungblud</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-prodigy">The Prodigy</a>已确认为头条新闻。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/the-offspring-courtney-love-sex-pistols-let-the-bad-times-roll-2888615"><b>摇滚乐会杀死脑细胞吗？！ - 子孙后代</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>即将到来的摇滚音乐节将于今年夏天晚些时候回归，举办时间为 6 月 12 日至 15 日，地点为捷克赫拉德茨克拉洛韦的 Park 360。</p><p>现在，组织者公布了将在活动中表演的新艺术家名单，其中包括三位新的头条新闻。其中包括将登上舞台为开幕之夜（7 月 12 日）拉开帷幕的 The Prodigy 和将在第二天成为头条新闻的 The Offspring。</p><p>以 2024 年最后一个头条新闻结束音乐节的人选也已确定为 Yungblud，他将于周六（7 月 15 日）与先前宣布的艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pendulum">Pendulum</a> （将演奏深夜曲目）和 Kaizers Orchestra 一起登上舞台。</p><p>这三位新宣布的演员加入了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bring-me-the-horizon">Bring Me The Horizo​​n</a>乐队，此前曾被透露为 7 月 11 日星期五的头条新闻。</p><p>目前确认出现在今年晚些时候的 Chezhian 音乐节的其他乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/enter-shikari">Enter Shikari</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-omens">Bad Omens</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wargasm">Wargasm</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sum-41">Sum 41——</a>后者将在该国演出，作为告别巡演的一部分，</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bombay-bicycle-club">《Bombay Bicycle Club</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soft-play">《Soft Play》</a> 、《Alien Weaponry》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/thy-art-is-murder">《Thy Art Is Murder</a> 》和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-amazons">《The Amazons》</a>也已锁定在 2024 年版，此外还有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hanabie">《Hanabie</a> 》、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hoobastank">《Hoobastank》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/royal-republic">《Royal Republic》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idkhow">《iDKHOW》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/against-the-current">《Against The Current》</a> 。</p><p>查看下面的节日海报中的当前阵容，并<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Frock-for-people-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F3009505" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处购买门票</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3565587" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3565587" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3565587" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster.jpg" alt="Rock For People 2024 年阵容海报" width="2000" height="1125" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster-400x225.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster-800x450.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster-696x392.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster-1392x783.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Rock-For-People-Poster-1068x601.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3565587" class="wp-caption-text"> Rock For People 2024 年阵容海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>去年，第一批将在 Rock For People 2024 上演出的艺术家首次公开，当时《Bring Me The Horizo​​n》被确认为头条新闻，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/corey-taylor">科里·泰勒 (Corey Taylor)</a>和艾薇儿·拉维尼 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/avril-lavigne">Avril Lavigne